  "text": "(Image credit: Christy) At this time of the year it's very common to refresh your space, but amongst the spring cleaning blitz, make sure you take some time to invest in some self care. Refreshing those everyday necessities with a touch of luxury will make every bath and bed routine feel more elevated and indulgent, and with our exclusive discount code with Christy, you can indulge in the finest towels, bedding and accessories for less.Christy has led the British towel and bed linen market for 175 years, renowned for their exceptional quality and elegant heritage designs that truly stand the test of time. With the launch of the Christy spring sale we've teamed up with them to offer you an exclusive 12% off all orders - and that can also be applied on top of sale items.To help you get started, we've selected a few of our favourite items available on Christy right now.What to buy from ChristyThese luxurious options are just a few of the pieces you can pick up from Christy using our exclusive discount code... There's nothing like a new throw to brighten up your bedding, and this plush design will add both ultimate comfort and luxury. The smooth cotton quilted velvet is available in 10 rich jewel inspired tones, and if you love a bit of co-ordination then you can also pick up the matching cushions. Scallop Edge Duvet and Pillowcase Set Scalloping is well and truly having a design moment, and this silky cotton sateen duvet and pillowcase set is the perfect balance of style and elegance. As well as being super soft and smooth on your skin, we love the subtle embroidered trim, which comes in your choice of silver, white, matcha green and fire red. One of the most classic towel options from Christy, this beloved design is crafted from 100% Egyptian cotton for a fluffiness that endures over time, wash after wash. The towels are available in every size from face cloths and bath mats, and you can choose from 13 stylish colours. This perennial bestseller has proven its quality with its top-notch absorbency, meaning both you and the towel dry in no time. The really clever thing is the innovative way the cotton was spun, which allows the towel to bloom after washing for extra fluffiness. You can choose from 12 colourways and shapes, and sizes to suit. This spring, invest in both your home and yourself with the Christy sale, and make sure to use our exclusive discount code to benefit from an additional 12% off your luxurious new purchases, too. Sign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.",
